      • extend

        public static PrefixMap extend(PrefixMap pmap)
        Creates a new prefix map which is an extension of an existing prefix map

        This differs from using one of the various create methods since it does not copy the existing prefix map, rather it maintains both a local map and the existing map. All operations favour the local map but defer to the existing map if the local map cannot fulfil a request.

        Parameters:
        pmap - Prefix Map to extend
        Returns:
        Prefix Map
